{"tid":2234811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中槍健仔疑認暴動罪 可保釋 12月22號再訊","createTime":"2020-10-08T07:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T09:46:16.000Z","uid":22556,"like":28,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"54061f3b309184f986bcfda5279ca2caca8a29f8","tid":2234811,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:22:18.000Z","msg":"18歲中五男生「健仔」曾志健去年10月1日在荃灣遭警員實彈槍傷，事後被控一項暴動罪及兩項襲警罪；當日跑到中槍「健仔」身旁大叫「救人先」的理工大學博士生亦被控暴動。兩人的案件今在區域法院提訊，控方申請將案押後，指需與辯方商討案情，「想達成共識同案情調整，言下之意，第一被告（「健仔」）之後應該會認罪」，案件押後至12月22再訊，兩人准以同樣條件保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Hs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=7c1839bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA%2F&h=38beef23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA/</a>"},{"pid":"c3de7aaa974acfdd76c875451c519be022435809","tid":2234811,"uid":67590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad4b1eb2ee921724d6a3b2594380b34eb9d3239","tid":2234811,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84de0e9a18245ceb8a5080c156fb972cb5478da8","tid":2234811,"uid":67590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcccc3313d8e9cf41bfff1a6ecb98ee14ffdbad5","tid":2234811,"uid":1072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a279e79669fffc0d66fc20098eeba4239da14f6","tid":2234811,"uid":291921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy